<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>INews - Home</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/1a02557296.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<style>
  .hero-card {
    position: relative;
    border: none;
    background-color: transparent;
  }
  .hero-card .card-img {
    filter: brightness(0.6); /* Darken image to make text pop */
  }
  .hero-card .card-img-overlay {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }
  
  /* Added this to make all content images have the same aspect ratio */
  .content-img {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-light navbar-light shadow-sm sticky-top">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <span class="navbar-brand mb-0 h1">INews</span>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
      <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#">World</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#">Politics</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="container-fluid p-0">
  <div class="card hero-card text-white">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508921340877-ba5760F62f08?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500" class="card-img" alt="Hero Image" style="max-height: 60vh; object-fit: cover;">
    <div class="card-img-overlay">
      <h1 class="display-3">Stay Informed</h1>
      <p class="lead">Your daily source for the latest news and dispatches.</p>
      <a href="news?id=in">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg">Read Today's News</button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">

  <div class="row g-5 my-4 d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2>Coverage</h2>
      <p>News serves as a crucial mechanism for keeping the public informed about current events and important developments. It encompasses a broad range of topics, including politics, economics, science, technology, culture, and more. News outlets... strive to provide accurate and timely information...</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <img class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm content-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504711434969-e33886168f5c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800" alt="News Coverage">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-5 my-4 d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h2>Dispatches</h2>
      <p>The evolution of news media has been marked by significant changes... The rise of digital platforms and social media has transformed the landscape, allowing for real-time updates... While this shift has made news more accessible, it has also introduced challenges...</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
      <img class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm content-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495020689067-958852a7765e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800" alt="News Dispatches">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-5 my-4 d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2>Reports</h2>
      <p>In addition to reporting facts, news organizations often play a role in shaping public opinion... Through investigative journalism and in-depth reporting, the media can highlight issues that might otherwise go unnoticed, prompting discussions and actions...</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <img class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm content-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543269664-76c013EA3e07?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800" alt="News Reports">
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>

<footer class="bg-dark text-white pt-4 pb-2">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <ul class="list-unstyled list-inline social">
          <li class="list-inline-item">
            <a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook fa-2x mx-2"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li class="list-inline-item">
            <a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter fa-2x mx-2"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li class="list-inline-item">
            <a href="#" class="text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram fa-2x mx-2"></i></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="bg-light">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <p class="small">&copy; 2020-2029 INews. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

